Abuja – Veteran Nigeria singer, Timi Dakolo and his wife Busola Dakolo seem not to bothered about the current court case against Pastor Biodun Fatoyinbo as they both enjoy time out. The lovely couple who has not been shy in showing fans how much they love one another as they constantly post each other picture on social media took to their IG page to share a dazzling pictures of themselves. The picture came with this interesting script as seen below:“Husband: Baby I will be going to London tomorrow.Me: Good, call them now to buy another ticket. This time I am coming with you. You will need me around.  Husband: How about the children?Me: I just called my sister, handled.Ladies and gentlemen, London is cold and beautiful.” Source